5. RUNNING ENTERPRISE DATABASE CONTAINERS (MySQL Layer)
-------------------------------------------------------
# Spawning isolated database service utilizing explicit environment variables:
$ sudo docker run -d -p 3306:3306 --name shubh-mysql-container -e MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD=mysecurepassword mysql:8.0

Attributes Analysis:
  -p 3306:3306   --> Binds local laptop host network port directly into MySQL socket layer.
  -e             --> Environment Variable injection mechanism defining core credentials.

Full Topology Status:
$ sudo docker ps
Parallel active runtime stacks verified (Nginx Web Gateway + MySQL Core Database Node).
===================================================================

